mayisi 11  arturi conspekty

vim-i hramaneri rejimi hramannery

:w  -> save
:q  -> quiting the vim(Important!: save the changes between exiting)
:wq -> writing or saving and exiting from vim
:e  -> witching between files inside vim(if the file does not exist vim is creathing)
:r  -> copying all the content from the selected file to the current file(starting from cursor)
:bn -> switch to the next file
:bp -> switching to the previous file

yy  -> yanking(copying the selected part of file)
p -> paste the copied text to the file
dd -> Deleting the line where the cursor is (Works both in Visual or Command Mode)

ctrl + v -> in visual block mode we select the block then type C it removes and we entering an insert mode then anyting you want you type after ESC it repeats for each line

insert mode-um 
ctrl+p -> !NOTE(In insert Mode) Completes the word for example (Co -> Code) Auto Complete

:%s/helo/barev/g  -> replaces the (all) old words to the new word
:3,8s/enbaryvoryzumenqpoxenq/inchnemuzumpoxem/g - replaces (all) old words from range of lines to new word(from 1 - 10)
:1;3;7/enbaryvoryzumenqpoxenq/inchnemuzumpoxem/g - replaces (all) old words in specified lines(1 and 5)
:%s/new/old/gc -> replaces (all) old words in all text and asks for confirumation



terminali vrai keyboardery(stexnashari hnarqnery)
terminali vra

MAYISI 8    DAS 9 DASAXOSUTYUN
ALT+F   - bary ach mi-mi bar
ALT+B   - bary dsax mi-mi bar
CTRL+F  - tary ach mi-mi tar
CTRL+B  - tary dsax mi-mi tar

ALT+E   - toxi verj
ALT+A   - toxi skizb

CTRL+T  - tary dsaxi tari het texerov poxuma
ALT+T   - bary dsaxi bari het texerov poxuma

CTRL+U  - cursoric dsax sax toxy jnjuma
CTRL+K  - cursoric aj sax toxy jnjuma
CTRL+Y  - PASTA-a anum jnjacsy

ALT+U   -  cursori texic depi aj amoxj bary dardsnuma mecsatar cusory tanelov bari verj
ALT+L   - cursori texic depi aj amoxj bary dardsnuma poqratar cusory tanelov bari verj
ALT+C   - cursori texic depi aj amoxj bary dardsnuma poqratar isk araji tary mecsatar cusory tanelov bari verj

   ||
